theorem interior_closure_interior_closure_eq_inter_closure
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    interior (closure (interior (closure A))) = interior (closure A) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  ·
    have hSub : closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A := by
      have : (interior (closure A) : Set X) ⊆ closure A := interior_subset
      exact closure_mono this
    exact interior_mono hSub
  ·
    have hOpen : IsOpen (interior (closure A)) := isOpen_interior
    have hIncl : (interior (closure A) : Set X) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) :=
      subset_closure
    exact interior_maximal hIncl hOpen

theorem P2_interior_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    Topology.P2 (interior (closure A)) := by
  have hOpen : IsOpen (interior (closure A)) := isOpen_interior
  exact Topology.P2_of_open hOpen
